			<guid><![CDATA[https://forum.dlrp.eu/forum/index.php?thread/11533-bewerbung-f%C3%BCr-das-lsmd/]]></guid>
						<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><strong><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 23pt;"><span style="color:rgb(0,255,0);">LSMD - Bewerbung</span></span></span></strong></p><p><span style="color:#FFFFFF;"><br><br></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 19pt;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">-------------------------------------</span></span></span></strong></p><p><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">Guten Tag, </span></span></span></p><p><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">Hiermit bewerbe ich mich als Mdler beim LSMD:</span></span></span></p><p><span style="color:#FFFFFF;"><br></span></p><p><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 20pt;"><span style="color:#00FF00;">Inhaltsverzeichnis</span></span></span><span style="color:#FFFFFF;"><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 20pt;"><span></span></span></span><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 20pt;"><span></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style="color:#FFFFFF;"><br><br></span></p><p><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 19pt;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">IC</span></span></span></p><p><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 19pt;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">OOC</span></span></span></p><p><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 19pt;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">Stärken / Schwächen</span></span></span></p><p><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 19pt;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">Warum möchte ich zum MD</span></span></span></p><p><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 19pt;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">Lizenzen</span></span></span></p><p><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 19pt;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">Schlusswort</span></span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 19pt;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">-------------------------------------</span></span></span></strong></p><p><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 22pt;"><span style="color:#00FF00;">Ic Infos</span></span></span></p><p><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 13pt;"><span style="color:#00FF00;"><span></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style="color:#FFFFFF;"><br></span><span style="color:#FFFFFF;"><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 13pt;">Guten Tag, mein Name ist Kenny Gezo und ich bin 21 Jahre alt. Geboren bin ich am 10.10.2000</span></span></span></p><p>Ich bin sehr gerne in der Stadt unterwegs und lerne die Mitbürger kennen.</p><p><strong><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 19pt;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">-------------------------------------</span></span></span></strong></p><p><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 19pt;"><span style="color:#00FF00;">OOC Informationen</span></span></span></p><p><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 13pt;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">Hey, mein Name ist Kenny, und ich bin 17 Jahre alt und komme aus Bayern.</span></span></span></p><p><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 13pt;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">Am Tag spiele ich circa 3-8 Stunden auf DLRP.</span></span></span></p><p><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 13pt;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">Roleplay Erfahrung habe ich in anderen Spielen sammeln können ca. 1600 Stunden Spielzeit in FiveM</span></span></span></p><p><span style="color:#FFFFFF;"><strong><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 19pt;">-------------------------------------</span></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="color:#00FF00;"><strong><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;">Meine Stärken sind:</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;"> </span></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 13pt;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">[+] Bin freundlich und nett mit meinen Mitmenschen.</span></span></span></p><p><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 13pt;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">[+] Ich kann genau auf den Punkt kommen wenn es drauf ankommt.</span></span></span></p><p><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 13pt;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">[+] Ich lerne sehr schnell.</span></span></span></p><p><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 13pt;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">[+] ich bin sehr Kommunikationsfähig</span></span></span></p><p><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 13pt;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">[+] Ich gehe mit jedem Respektvoll um</span></span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 19pt;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">-------------------------------------</span></span></span></strong></p><p><span style="color:#FFFFFF;"><br></span></p><p><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 17pt;"><span style="color:#00FF00;">Meine Schwächen sind:</span></span></span></p><p><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 13pt;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">[-] Zögerlich</span></span></span></p><p><span style="color:rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 13pt;font-family:Merriweather, serif;">[-] In manchen Situationen leicht überfordert</span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 19pt;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">-------------------------------------</span></span></span></strong></p><p><strong><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 16pt;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;"><span></span></span></span></span></strong></p><p><strong><span style="color:#FFFFFF;"><br></span></strong><span style="color:#00FF00;"><strong><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 16pt;">Warum möchte ich zum MD</span></span></strong></span><span style="color:#FFFFFF;"><strong><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 16pt;"></span></span></strong></span></p><p><strong><br></strong><strong></strong></p><span style="font-family: Merriweather, serif"><span style="font-size: 16px;">Da ich einfach mal was neues in diesen Staat machen möchte und den Menschen helfen möchte.</span></span><p><br></p><p><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">Durch meine Erfahrungen als Mdler denke ich bin ich der geeignete Mdler für das LSMD.</span></span></span></p><p><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;"><span></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style="color:#FFFFFF;"><br></span><strong><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="color: #ffffff"><span style="font-size: 19pt;">-------------------------------------</span></span></span></strong></p><p><strong><span style="color: #00ff00"><span style="">Lizenzen</span></span></strong><strong>
</strong></p><p><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">PKW</span></strong><strong>
</strong></p><p><strong><span style="font-family:'open sans', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 13px;"><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 19pt;">-------------------------------------</span></span></span></span></strong><strong></strong></p><p><strong><br></strong><strong></strong></p><p><span style="color:#FFFFFF;"><br></span></p><p><span style="color:#00FF00;"><strong><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 16pt;">Mit freundlichen Grüßen</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 16pt;"><span></span></span></span></strong></span></p><p><strong><span style="color:#FFFFFF;"><br></span></strong></p><p><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="color:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="">Kenny<br></span><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Kontaktmöglichkeiten:</span></span></span></p><p><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">Discord : Kenxy#9735</span></span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family:Merriweather, serif;"><span style="font-size: 19pt;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">-------------------------------------</span></span></span></strong></p>]]></content:encoded>
